(101, 1, '2024-12-17 12:30:51', '2024-12-17 12:30:51', 'Jumper wires are essential components used in electronics and Arduino projects to create connections between different circuit elements, such as Arduino boards, sensors, and other components. These wires come with pre-attached male or female connectors, making it easy to plug them into a breadboard or an Arduino\'s pin headers. Jumper wires allow for quick, flexible, and secure connections without the need for soldering, making them ideal for prototyping and testing electronic circuits. They are commonly used in projects involving sensors, motors, LEDs, and more, providing a simple and organized way to link components together.', 'Jumper Wires (40 pcs)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'jumper-wires-40-pcs', '', '', '2024-12-19 19:16:14', '2024-12-19 19:16:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?post_type=product&#038;p=101', 0, 'product', '', 0),
