(199, 1, '2024-12-18 21:15:58', '2024-12-18 21:15:58', 'The USB cable for Arduino connects an Arduino board to a computer for power, data transfer, and program uploading. Compatible with various Arduino models, it ensures a stable and fast connection.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nTypes: USB-A to USB-B.\r\nLength: Typically 1 to 2 meters.\r\nCompatibility: Works with Arduino Uno, Mega, Nano, etc.\r\nDurable Materials: Robust connectors and flexible cable.', 'USB Cable for Arduino', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'usb-cable-for-arduino', '', '', '2024-12-19 18:31:12', '2024-12-19 18:31:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?post_type=product&#038;p=199', 0, 'product', '', 0),
